  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The Brody belt may help improve quality of life in patients using urinary drainage bags.
      PURPOSE: This clinical trial studies the Brody belt in improving the quality of life in
      patients using urinary drainage bags.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
